 1â†’//! Kraken WebSocket V2 client library.
 2â†’//!
 3â†’//! Provides typed models and async WebSocket functions for subscribing to
 4â†’//! Kraken's public market data channels (ticker, book, trades, candles,
 5â†’//! instruments, and level-3 orders).
 6â†’
